                          General Information

  LibSoup-SOAP is a library to add SOAP support to LibSoup.

  LibSoup-SOAP is a free and open source software under the General
Public License version 3.  Check the "License" section below for more
information. See the file 'COPYING' for license terms and conditions.

  The official web site is <http://libsoup-soap.sourceforge.net/>.


                              Installation

  LibSoup-SOAP's dependencies are LibSoup, GLib and LibXML2.

  LibSoup-SOAP is tested to work for Linux and Microsoft Windows
operating systems.

  See the file 'INSTALL' for compiling instructions.


